{Once more, SOUTH has the same hand as Deals 1 and 2.

This time NORTH has a very poor hand without any chance of making game. However, he should bid 
4\S anyway.

It is very likely that the opponents can make 4\H if East gets the 
opportunity to get into the bidding. Hopefully the 4\S bid will shut him out, and 4\S probably 
won't go down more than a couple of tricks.}

